Description:
On the battlefield you see the lizardmen fight against the crocomen, after a while something catches your attention, this is not a war but something more organized, rather it seems like a competition to see which tribe is the strongest.

Both sides see you and they don't seem to care that you are there, in fact they encourage you to join their side.

The highlight of the battle is about to begin and the two leaders along with their best soldiers will face off.
DescriptionAction: What do you want to do?
